#Dumb Terminal Firewall Script
DTfw - Firewall

a simple to robust script to make using IPTables http://www.netfilter.org/projects/iptables/ easier.
by: MikereDD & Veekahn

Syntax Features:
 start, stop, restart, save, restore, and status

Extra Features:
 Works with: SSHGuard, more to come...

Dynamic Host Updater:
Added a dynamic host updater script/module.
Update 1 or several hostnames that use Dynamic DNS.
Email localhost and or a non-local email address what hostname, old ip/new ip and time/date.

Features to Come:
 Admin Tools: better logging and admin scripts-tools.
